LuaScript:
--[[Make all guids in this objectTable as non-interactable 
meaning they cannot be manipulated in any way by the players.]]--

--Replace GUIDs with your own!
objectTable = { "be127b", "eb52c4" }

function onLoad()
    --Loop entries in the object table setting interactable to false
    	for i=1, #objectTable, 1 do	
        		obj = getObjectFromGUID(objectTable[i])
        		if obj ~= nil then
            			obj.interactable = false
        		end
    	end
end
